Subsequently, through the use of the innovative technology Elumina8 the new Glk will be illuminated at different times in all its details, then recomposed into a single image.
Undoubtedly Mercedes with this advertisement is trying to introduce something new in the stereotypical field of automotive communication.
Will this formula arouse the interest of future buyers? We will see.
